# Sub-agent orchestration — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

When to fan out to sub-agents, how to budget tokens, and the anti-patterns.

## Custom agents
Defined in `.claude/agents/`. The starter set:
- `code-reviewer` — reviews a diff across the five axes + project gates.
- `docs-drift-detector` — sweeps for doc-code drift.
- `test-engineer` — designs tests + maps coverage to decision rows.
